
//Steps for installation
1)npm init -y : make a default package.json---All the libraries are listed in package.json
npm-----node packet manager
2) npm install typescript --save-dev-------read package.json and bring all the library to node modules
3) npx tsc --init --rootDir src --outDir build--------make a configuration file
--"rootDir": "src" ------  Specify the root folder within your source files. 
--"outDir": "build"-----Specify an output folder for all emitted files. 
4)Create a folder with folder name src and a file inside it as script.tsc
5)npx tsc --watch-------a folder named build is made with js extension

//To see output in console
1) Save the code in typescript file, eg: Day5.ts
2)npx tsc --watch
3)a folder named build is made with js extension,eg: Day5.js
4) cd build
5) node Day5.js
